PrecisAppointment of BRAHIM ACHTOUTAL as Consul General of Canada in Istanbul (Republic of Turkey); PATRICE COUSINEAU as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Tunisia; MARK GLAUSER as High Commissioner for Canada in Australia with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Palau, with residence in Canberra; and SANDRA SHADDICK as Consul General of Canada in Monterrey (United Mexican States).
